column5: all I see is a close resemblance to my mother-in-laws hair in the morning
I was going to say I see medusa.LOL Brian, I think its time to cut down>LOL
Puff goes the magic dragon....

First off,what a very very quiet morning.Not a turkey cluck anywhere or deer to be seen or red squirl.Very quiet. So I decided to push the bush a mile and a half back. Didnt even jump a deer anywhere.So I just sat a few times and took some pics.  Cold enough to freeze the water ponds.    Now do you  see what I see? These blown over tree roots have been around for awhile,but I stared for a bit and I see a rotten salmon and a preistoric gar.    Salmon top left.    And the gar     On my way out ,I went to visit that scrap and rub.He,s been back.Maybe that spray of doe got him excited as he ripped it up good.
Why are you thinkin about fishing, when your out huntin?  Musta been a real quiet morning..  Any signs of more gangs doggin your bush?
I want some of what you are smoking. Looks like tree roots to me. Sitting quiet in the bush does strange things to a man's mind.
lol you beat me to it !!
Double LOL, was staring at these pics and about to say the same thing.  Did you lick any frogs by the frozen water ponds?? LOL
The only answer to that is a Simpsons quote "I'm not, not licking frogs"
as been said before.. remember ..puff puff pass....... you have to pass
I don't think he was smoking...eating mushroom's maybe...
I'm sure Timothy Leary would have seen it too......
Good thing I didnt tell ya,ll I thought I seen preditor. I then realised it was my floaters acting up.  First off,havent partaked in that stuff since high school  And I never passed
White Rabbit on the far side over dare
I thought i saw it  ...10mins later.... NO i dont see nothing..

With apologies to Mr. Service.  There are strange things seen in the midnight sun By the men who moil for deer; The atv trails have their secret tales That would make your blood run cold; The Northern Lights have seen queer sights, But the queerest they ever did see Was that day on the marge of Lake Lebarge I couldn't see the same as Brian B.
The mrs,s sees a face,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,Ok please pass.

Well my OFC friends. This is the first stages of our dear friend going nuts.  Brian, I stared at it until I went cross eyed and got a headache. I beleive you may have a leak in that exhaust on your truck and its seeping into the cab. Can you please trace out the Salmon and the gar before I join you in that land of sunshine and Lolipops.
Maybe I should of closed the cap on that synthitic doe urin.  Here ya go,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,, I dont see it so clearly now   .  You had to be there.
HMMMM and I let you hunt in my yard while you're on your meds....
I see a pristine white rubber room in you're future...
I thought of any OFC member,you of all, would of seen it,,,,,,,,,,,
LOL! and that is why we are peas from the same pod! I will be you're roommate in said rubber room... saying have we had enough fun yet!
